Choco is a MiniPay-native USDC -> KESm remittance app on Celo Mainnet. It
integrates with third-party protocols (Mento, Uniswap V3, MiniPay) and uses
open-source libraries (viem, ethers, React, Vite, and others), each distributed
under their own licenses.
